{
  "title": "rho-kit / Service overview",
  "uid": "rhokit-service-overview",
  "tags": ["rho-kit", "overview"],
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "time": { "from": "now-1h", "to": "now" },
  "refresh": "30s",
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "namespace",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": "Prometheus",
        "query": "label_values(http_requests_total, namespace)",
        "refresh": 2
      },
      {
        "name": "service",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": "Prometheus",
        "query": "label_values(http_requests_total{namespace=\"$namespace\"}, service)",
        "refresh": 2
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "title": "Service health (1=up)",
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "max(up{namespace=\"$namespace\", service=\"$service\"})", "legendFormat": "up" }
      ],
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 0 }
    },
    {
      "title": "Request rate (req/s)",
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total{namespace=\"$namespace\", service=\"$service\"}[5m]))" }
      ],
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 0 }
    },
    {
      "title": "Error rate (4xx + 5xx, req/s)",
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "sum(rate(http_errors_total{namespace=\"$namespace\", service=\"$service\"}[5m]))" }
      ],
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 0 }
    },
    {
      "title": "Latency p99 (s)",
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (le) (rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket{namespace=\"$namespace\", service=\"$service\"}[5m])))" }
      ],
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 0 }
    },
    {
      "title": "Linked dashboards",
      "type": "text",
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**RED & runtime**\n- [HTTP RED](/d/rhokit-http-red)\n- [gRPC RED](/d/rhokit-grpc-red)\n- [Go runtime](/d/rhokit-runtime-go)\n\n**Infrastructure**\n- [DB pool](/d/rhokit-db-pool) — Postgres/MySQL connection pool\n- [Redis](/d/rhokit-redis) — commands, pool, reconnects\n- [Storage (S3 + SFTP)](/d/rhokit-storage)\n- [Outbox relay](/d/rhokit-outbox)\n\n**Skipped (no metrics yet)**\n- AMQP messaging — buffered publisher uses callback hooks rather than Prometheus collectors. Add when `infra/messaging` exposes Prometheus collectors.\n- Ratelimit — `httpx/middleware/ratelimit` does not currently emit metrics."
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 12, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 4 }
    }
  ]
}
